ad member flashbangs a room and another then clears it out, cannot be done in an efficient way) isnt possible.Also pretty much all the guns are the same. There are assault rifles, a P90 sub machine gun, maybe one or two marksman rilfes (semi-automatics), three shotguns that are only affective in the right situation, ONE sniper rifle, and ONE machine gun available. everything else is an assualt rifle, WHICH ALL FEEL THE SAME. The other guns dont even matter once you get the TAR assault rifle as it pretty much wins u the game. Also the MG kinda sucks as it fires rapidly dealing maybe 5 damage if u even hit the person but then again the time for moving lasts like 10 seconds which isnt enough time to kill one guy, making it ulitmately unsatisfying."
