,Recommended,266130,33315267,Posted: 6 July,all,dewbertb,"I usually wait until I finish a game to review it, but this one has earned a thumbs up from me already! I got this game at a great price during the Summer Sale (90% off!) - but could see having some misgivings if I had paid full price. I have been really grooving on turn-based strategy games recently and this game scratches my itch well!! It's a bit like Rainbow Six in that you can choose between SEALs, SAS, Spetsnaz, etc. You can also customize the weapon (including optics, IR, grip, trigger) and equipment on each squad member. I like the variety of mission locations, multiple modes for each location (Terrorist Hunt, Bomb Defusal, and Escape Plan), that each mission takes 5 minutes or less to complete, and that difficulty & breaching technique can be changed. I found this game to offer plenty of replayability to try different tactics or attempt to improve ratings.I recommend this game to any turn-based strategy fans... just maybe wait until it's on sale!!"
